<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">大概是让我和八九寺小姐尽兴地玩了一阵的时间</font>

268
00:12:01,870 --> 00:12:03,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你们对着昏睡的我做了些什么啊</font>

269
00:12:04,460 --> 00:12:07,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">话说居然叫她八九寺小姐  你俩到底是有多要好啊</font>

270
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:11,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">具体说的话是一晚上  从傍晚开始一直到现在</font>

271
00:12:11,940 --> 00:12:14,070
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">差不多快十二小时了吧</font>

272
00:12:14,390 --> 00:12:15,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">十二小时</font>

273
00:12:15,470 --> 00:12:15,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（那还真是睡了好久啊）</font>

274
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:22,600
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">小心起见  上下移动它就不会追过来的法则也只不过是经验之谈</font>

275
00:12:22,990 --> 00:12:26,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说到底也就只限于现在的情况  下次能不能成功就不得而知了</font>

276
00:12:27,180 --> 00:12:32,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯  且不说经验  那个「黑暗」根本就不遵循法则</font>

277
00:12:33,110 --> 00:12:33,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">它到底是什么东西</font>

278
00:12:33,990 --> 00:12:34,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（倒不如一直追着还让人感到舒服一点）</font>

279
00:12:34,790 --> 00:12:35,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">八九寺呢</font>

280
00:12:41,540 --> 00:12:41,910
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（八九寺看上去还是非常健康）</font>

281
00:12:42,990 --> 00:12:43,370
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（触碰着确认一下确实没错）</font>

282
00:12:44,450 --> 00:12:44,790
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（相当健康）</font>

283
00:12:45,110 --> 00:12:50,190
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那么  要怎么做呢  现在连这里是哪儿都不知道</font>

284
00:12:51,040 --> 00:12:51,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（当然没信号）</font>

285
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:55,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽然很想作出反击  但是反击对它有效么</font>

286
00:12:56,230 --> 00:13:00,460
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而且那个东西是不是真的针对我们其实也不清楚</font>

287
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:04,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">针对小忍的推测  说是经验之谈的话也只不过是经验之谈</font>

288
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:08,810
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">作为反击的基准  首先要做的是开口问</font>

289
00:13:09,060 --> 00:13:09,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">问？</font>

290
00:13:09,800 --> 00:13:11,030
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就是收集情报</font>

291
00:13:11,670 --> 00:13:15,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那家伙出现前一刻我说的话你忘了吗</font>

292
00:13:16,060 --> 00:13:19,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我不是说过  那个并非怪异的现象  有人是知道的</font>

293
00:13:19,740 --> 00:13:19,910
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（就像书签一样 —— 插了进来）</font>

294
00:13:19,910 --> 00:13:20,030
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（看来我故意演坏人还是有意义的）</font>

295
00:13:20,030 --> 00:13:20,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（连你也起哄）</font>

296
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:20,370
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（哪怕是由谁来说都好）</font>

297
00:13:20,370 --> 00:13:20,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}找我有事的话就像刚才那样</font>

298
00:13:20,370 --> 00:13:20,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}用吻来叫我就行了嘛</font>

299
00:13:20,370 --> 00:13:20,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}真是个害羞的孩子</font>

300
00:13:20,530 --> 00:13:20,700
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（怪异杀手）</font>

301
00:13:20,700 --> 00:13:20,870
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（由凭丧神引发的「不能浪费」的精神吗）</font>

302
00:13:20,870 --> 00:13:21,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（卧烟伊豆湖）</font>

303
00:13:21,470 --> 00:13:22,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">卧烟…</font>

304
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:26,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">卧烟伊豆湖  只要和那个人询问就好了吗</font>

305
00:13:26,990 --> 00:13:29,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">好像是影缝小姐的熟人吧</font>

306
00:13:29,560 --> 00:13:34,230
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也就是说  首先要向身为联络人的影缝小姐打听情报了</font>

307
00:13:35,060 --> 00:13:37,460
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">斧乃木妹妹  工作不要紧吗</font>

308
00:13:37,710 --> 00:13:39,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当然要紧了</font>

309
00:13:39,220 --> 00:13:42,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不过  现在这状况也没法放心地回去工作啊</font>

310
00:13:43,630 --> 00:13:45,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我也不是那么无情</font>

311
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:48,590
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">能和影缝小姐取得联系吗</font>

312
00:13:49,070 --> 00:13:53,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">作为最后手段  还是有几个可以联系到姐姐的办法的</font>

313
00:13:53,740 --> 00:13:56,790
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但这些办法在这深山里都没法用</font>

314
00:13:57,060 --> 00:13:59,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你们不能通过心灵感应什么的沟通一下吗</font>

315
00:13:59,390 --> 00:14:00,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">很不巧</font>

316
00:14:00,270 --> 00:14:02,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我们的联系并没有那么紧密</font>

317
00:14:02,860 --> 00:14:06,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只能等下山后  用电话或是邮件什么的联系她了</font>

318
00:14:07,790 --> 00:14:07,950
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（但是）</font>

319
00:14:07,950 --> 00:14:08,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（姐姐她到了万不得已的时候）</font>

320
00:14:08,200 --> 00:14:08,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（应该是会毫不犹豫地抛弃我的）</font>

321
00:14:10,260 --> 00:14:12,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">话说回来  鬼哥哥</font>

322
00:14:12,620 --> 00:14:17,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是不是该把怪异杀手从影子里拉出来了</font>

323
00:14:17,090 --> 00:14:17,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（哎？）</font>

324
00:14:17,780 --> 00:14:21,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不知她是讨厌和我说话  还是在悠闲地睡大觉</font>

325
00:14:21,620 --> 00:14:24,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">总之从在这里着陆到现在她都没出来过</font>

326
00:14:24,010 --> 00:14:24,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="28">{\an7}这么说来</font>

327
00:14:24,010 --> 00:14:24,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="28">{\an7}忍确实不在——不</font>

328
00:14:24,010 --> 00:14:24,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="28">{\an7}对于她不在场这件事</font>

329
00:14:24,010 --> 00:14:24,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="28">{\an7}我从一开始就察觉到了</font>

330
00:14:24,010 --> 00:14:24,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="28">{\an7}所以说</font>

331
00:14:24,010 --> 00:14:24,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="28">{\an7}我就自然而然地以为忍还在我的影子里——</font>

332
00:14:24,010 --> 00:14:24,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="28">{\an7}和斧乃木妹妹还有八九寺不同</font>

333
00:14:24,010 --> 00:14:24,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="28">{\an7}我和忍之间是不会「失散」的</font>

334
00:14:24,510 --> 00:14:24,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（通过影子）</font>

335
00:14:24,720 --> 00:14:25,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（通过心——）</font>

336
00:14:25,010 --> 00:14:25,350
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（通过存在本身，互相紧密联系着）</font>

337
00:14:25,480 --> 00:14:26,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">忍她？</font>

338
00:14:26,180 --> 00:14:26,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an7}我们不会分开——也就是说</font>

339
00:14:26,180 --> 00:14:26,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an7}在这里看不到忍的身影的话</font>

340
00:14:26,180 --> 00:14:26,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an7}归结为一种理所当然的理论，那家伙现在</font>

341
00:14:26,180 --> 00:14:26,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an7}肯定还是在我的影子里</font>

342
00:14:26,680 --> 00:14:26,890
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（——可是）</font>

343
00:14:26,890 --> 00:14:27,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（可是）</font>

344
00:14:27,180 --> 00:14:27,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（仔细想想的话又有点奇怪）</font>

345
00:14:27,780 --> 00:14:29,270
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为现在是夜晚</font>

346
00:14:29,270 --> 00:14:29,770
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an7}已经接近黎明</font>

347
00:14:29,270 --> 00:14:29,770
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an7}虽然不能算作午夜</font>

348
00:14:29,270 --> 00:14:29,770
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an7}但现在还是可以被归在「夜晚」的范畴</font>

349
00:14:29,270 --> 00:14:29,770
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an7}这一点是没有错的——</font>

350
00:14:29,770 --> 00:14:30,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（尚未天明）</font>

351
00:14:30,380 --> 00:14:31,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">可那又是为什么…</font>

352
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:33,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">为什么小忍没有醒</font>

353
00:14:34,670 --> 00:14:38,400
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">为什么…鬼哥哥  你就算问我…</font>

354
00:14:38,400 --> 00:14:38,650
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（强烈的不协调感）</font>

355
00:14:38,880 --> 00:14:39,550
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我也没法回答</font>

356
00:14:39,910 --> 00:14:43,410
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">或者说  也许是她讨厌我吧</font>

357
00:14:43,560 --> 00:14:44,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">的确</font>

358
00:14:44,640 --> 00:14:46,950
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">小忍是不喜欢你</font>

359
00:14:47,180 --> 00:14:48,600
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但仅凭这个理由</font>

360
00:14:48,760 --> 00:14:52,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">她应该不会在这个关键的时候如字面一般躲在影子里的</font>

361
00:14:52,590 --> 00:14:54,190
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">她不是这种人</font>

362
00:14:54,830 --> 00:14:56,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你还挺信赖她的</font>

363
00:14:59,820 --> 00:15:01,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那又是怎么回事</font>

364
00:15:02,420 --> 00:15:06,110
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽然我也不相信  但她会不会是在影子里晕过去了</font>

365
00:15:06,420 --> 00:15:09,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">或是因为什么理由受了重伤</font>

366
00:15:09,430 --> 00:15:12,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">在影子里也会受重伤吗</font>

367
00:15:13,100 --> 00:15:15,560
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那里就像忍的超空间一样</font>

368
00:15:15,790 --> 00:15:19,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">应该是不会发生物理性冲击的</font>

369
00:15:20,440 --> 00:15:20,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（虽说是月光映照下的浅影，但那确实是我的影子——）</font>

370
00:15:20,690 --> 00:15:21,070
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（忍应该就在那里面）</font>

371
00:15:21,070 --> 00:15:21,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不在就奇怪了——）</font>

372
00:15:24,470 --> 00:15:27,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">斧乃木妹妹  这样的话  就只有和你接吻一个办法了</font>

373
00:15:28,780 --> 00:15:30,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你是怎么得出这个结论的</font>

374
00:15:30,550 --> 00:15:35,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就像昨天一样  只能用这种行为的刺激来唤醒小忍</font>

375
00:15:35,620 --> 00:15:36,350
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只有接吻</font>

376
00:15:36,750 --> 00:15:37,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只有舌吻这一个办法了</font>

377
00:15:37,920 --> 00:15:38,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（没有其他办法）</font>

378
00:15:38,210 --> 00:15:38,550
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（只能靠双唇贴合）</font>

379
00:15:38,550 --> 00:15:39,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（没有其他选项！）</font>

380
00:15:39,520 --> 00:15:41,670
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果你非要这么做的话也可以</font>

381
00:15:42,060 --> 00:15:42,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但总觉得好讨厌</font>

382
00:15:43,050 --> 00:15:43,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（好讨厌）</font>

383
00:15:44,420 --> 00:15:44,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那个  阿良良木先生</font>

384
00:15:44,930 --> 00:15:45,890
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那个  阿良良木先生</font>

385
00:15:47,110 --> 00:15:48,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">什么嘛八九寺  你嫉妒了？</font>

386
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:51,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">要不把接吻的对象换成你也可以哦</font>

387
00:15:52,040 --> 00:15:54,390
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">既然你有这个想法早说不就行了</font>

388
00:15:55,440 --> 00:15:56,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">请你死一下  阿良良木先生</font>

389
00:15:57,230 --> 00:15:59,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">…不对  请你等一下  阿良良木先生</font>

390
00:16:00,200 --> 00:16:02,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">为什么我必须要等啊</font>

391
00:16:02,750 --> 00:16:04,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我正要和斧乃木妹妹接吻呢</font>

392
00:16:04,500 --> 00:16:08,080
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  阿良良木先生  就算你有无数个理由</font>

393
00:16:08,310 --> 00:16:12,040
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但在那之前  在那以前  关于忍小姐…</font>

394
00:16:12,540 --> 00:16:15,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就是说  其实她并不在影子里吧</font>

395
00:16:15,680 --> 00:16:16,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那个人  现在</font>

396
00:16:17,590 --> 00:16:19,170
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  怎么可能不在…</font>

397
00:16:19,170 --> 00:16:19,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（也许是在睡觉）</font>

398
00:16:19,420 --> 00:16:19,750
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（也许是失去了意识……）</font>

399
00:16:20,460 --> 00:16:21,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">鬼哥哥  让我试一下</font>

400
00:16:21,380 --> 00:16:22,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">鬼哥哥  让我试一下</font>

401
00:16:24,550 --> 00:16:25,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">斧乃木妹妹</font>

402
00:16:25,640 --> 00:16:27,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">闭嘴  现在正在调查</font>

