<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">可是  你并没有变成那样</font>

422
00:17:08,890 --> 00:17:09,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（……并没有变成那样……）</font>

423
00:17:09,430 --> 00:17:13,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">啊不  可是  关于我有没有失去吸血鬼特性</font>

424
00:17:13,300 --> 00:17:14,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你有能辨别出来的方法吗</font>

425
00:17:14,640 --> 00:17:14,890
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（身为式神——）</font>

426
00:17:14,890 --> 00:17:15,350
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（身为怪异）</font>

427
00:17:15,590 --> 00:17:16,600
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">斧乃木妹妹你有方法吗…</font>

428
00:17:16,780 --> 00:17:20,880
