00:17:37,390 --> 00:17:38,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">的确能看得见</font>

436
00:17:41,040 --> 00:17:41,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（那家伙现在）</font>

437
00:17:41,290 --> 00:17:41,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（并不在我的影子里这件事）</font>

438
00:17:41,630 --> 00:17:42,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（也是事实）</font>

439
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:43,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是吗</font>

