<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">用更准确的说法的话</font>

445
00:17:56,560 --> 00:17:59,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也许应该说是「联系已经被消灭」</font>

446
00:18:01,310 --> 00:18:03,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">拜那个「黑暗」与你的影子重合所赐</font>

447
00:18:03,980 --> 00:18:04,190
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（影子）</font>

448
00:18:04,190 --> 00:18:04,480
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（踩影子）</font>

449
00:18:04,480 --> 00:18:04,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（真成了踩影子游戏）</font>

450
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:09,780
