461
00:18:48,740 --> 00:18:48,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（必须快点和那家伙汇合）</font>

462
00:18:48,860 --> 00:18:49,110
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（必须快点向那家伙道歉）</font>

463
00:18:49,110 --> 00:18:49,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（想要向她道歉）</font>

464
00:18:49,700 --> 00:18:51,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">现在并不是最坏的局面</font>

465
00:18:51,490 --> 00:18:51,740
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（…不知道能不能哄她开心）</font>

466
00:18:51,740 --> 00:18:52,110
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（虽然不知道——）</font>

467
00:18:52,110 --> 00:18:52,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（但至少想要向她道歉）</font>

468
00:18:53,140 --> 00:18:55,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是啊  的确是这样</font>

469
00:18:55,330 --> 00:18:55,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（最重要的是，好想见到她）</font>

470
00:18:56,780 --> 00:18:56,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（无法原谅。无法原谅。）</font>

471
00:18:56,990 --> 00:18:57,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（居然敢）</font>

472
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:57,450
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（居然敢让小忍，遭受那种境遇——）</font>

473
00:18:58,190 --> 00:19:01,330
