474
00:19:01,550 --> 00:19:03,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我虽然能理解你的心情  鬼哥哥</font>

475
00:19:04,180 --> 00:19:05,170
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但不要着急</font>

476
00:19:05,170 --> 00:19:05,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不好）</font>

477
00:19:05,380 --> 00:19:05,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（头脑不听使唤）</font>

478
00:19:05,630 --> 00:19:06,040
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（行动一片混杂可怎么行）</font>

479
00:19:06,360 --> 00:19:11,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽然我也赞成下山  但在和怪异杀手汇合之前</font>

480
00:19:11,190 --> 00:19:12,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">应该先和姐姐取得联系</font>

481
00:19:13,120 --> 00:19:14,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">啊  是吗</font>

482
00:19:14,300 --> 00:19:14,550
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（顺序）</font>

483
00:19:14,550 --> 00:19:14,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（最优顺序）</font>

484
00:19:14,930 --> 00:19:15,390
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（必须选择这样的顺序）</font>

485
00:19:15,520 --> 00:19:16,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但不管怎么说</font>

486
00:19:17,190 --> 00:19:21,100
