487
00:19:21,590 --> 00:19:24,190
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  不是这样的  鬼哥哥</font>

488
00:19:24,640 --> 00:19:28,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">很遗憾  「多数例外规则·脱离版」已经没法再用了</font>

489
00:19:28,860 --> 00:19:29,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">呃  为什么</font>

