00:19:44,600 --> 00:19:48,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">鬼哥哥你现在  变弱了</font>

494
00:19:48,500 --> 00:19:51,340
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">并不仅仅是「多数例外规则·脱离版」</font>

495
00:19:51,900 --> 00:19:56,300
