499
00:20:10,600 --> 00:20:13,620
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吸血鬼的特性虽然没有消失  但正在减弱</font>

500
00:20:13,980 --> 00:20:17,070
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不死身也一样  虽然没有消失  但正在减弱</font>

501
00:20:17,070 --> 00:20:17,370
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不会是好事）</font>

502
00:20:17,370 --> 00:20:17,740
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（就像这样）</font>

503
00:20:17,740 --> 00:20:18,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（事态正在渐渐恶化）</font>

504
00:20:19,390 --> 00:20:24,300
