505
00:20:24,700 --> 00:20:27,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">既然切断了联系  相对地…</font>

506
00:20:27,560 --> 00:20:31,070
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  恐怕那边的吸血鬼度也在下降呢</font>

507
00:20:31,700 --> 00:20:32,700
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">连锁反应</font>

508
00:20:33,280 --> 00:20:36,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你们的关系就是这样的</font>

509
00:20:36,840 --> 00:20:37,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（没错）</font>

510
00:20:37,760 --> 00:20:37,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（就是这样的构造）</font>

511
00:20:38,220 --> 00:20:43,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就是说  不仅是我  小忍那边的状况也是急转直下</font>

512
00:20:44,100 --> 00:20:46,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是先冷静点  还没有结束</font>

513
00:20:47,320 --> 00:20:49,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">故事还在继续</font>

514
00:20:52,080 --> 00:20:54,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你和影缝小姐应该能用邮件之类的手段联系到吧</font>

