519
00:21:09,390 --> 00:21:13,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">还有火怜和月火都发了自报平安的邮件</font>

520
00:21:15,170 --> 00:21:15,670
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（因为不想让她们担心）</font>

521
00:21:15,670 --> 00:21:16,170
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（暂时不会回来  不用但心）</font>

522
00:21:16,420 --> 00:21:16,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（哼哼）</font>

523
00:21:19,300 --> 00:21:19,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（我也成长成懂得为他人着想的男人了）</font>

524
00:21:19,980 --> 00:21:20,870
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">阿良良木先生</font>

525
00:21:21,070 --> 00:21:22,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">怎么了  八九寺</font>

526
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:25,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">在你发信之后才说这些感觉有些那个</font>

527
00:21:25,400 --> 00:21:27,310
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">可你给羽川小姐她们发的邮件</font>

528
00:21:27,550 --> 00:21:30,610
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">内容里写的是「不用但心」</font>

529
00:21:31,950 --> 00:21:34,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">发信之后才说这些也太那个了吧！</font>

530
00:21:42,430 --> 00:21:45,700
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">鬼哥哥  手机的信号怎么样了</font>

531
00:21:46,120 --> 00:21:46,410
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（没有回信）</font>

532
00:21:47,260 --> 00:21:48,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">还是老样子  信号很弱</font>

533
00:21:49,260 --> 00:21:50,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">幸好不是完全没有信号</font>

534
00:21:51,420 --> 00:21:53,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">刚才还真是运气好呢</font>

535
00:21:53,500 --> 00:21:57,040
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是嘛  可是还没有收到影缝小姐的回复呢</font>

536
00:21:57,470 --> 00:21:57,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">哼</font>

537
00:21:58,460 --> 00:22:01,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那么  还是直接打过去比较好</font>

538
00:22:02,030 --> 00:22:03,670
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只好打扰一下附近的人家了</font>

